exports[`Session surfaces ŌĆö /help > renders in narrow width > help-narrow width 1`] = `
"[1mEstaCoda session commands[0m
ŌĆó /help: Show command help
ŌĆó /status: Show runtime, model, context, trust, memory, and skill status
ŌĆó /model: Show the active model and provider without changing saved setup state.
ŌĆó /switch: Switch to an existing session
ŌĆó /search: Search session history
ŌĆó /compact: Compact this in-session context
ŌĆó /reset: Start a fresh session and refresh the skill/config snapshot
ŌĆó /memory: Inspect promoted memory conclusions
ŌĆó /tools: Browse available tools grouped by toolset
ŌĆó /browser: Manage local browser/CDP connection
ŌĆó /skills: Browse commands and available skills
ŌĆó /packs: Manage packs (install, enable, disable, uninstall)
ŌĆó /reload-mcp: Reload MCP config and refresh MCP tools for this session
ŌĆó /resume: Show the latest interrupted-turn resume note
ŌĆó /approvals: Show current one-time, session, and persistent approvals
ŌĆó /revoke: Revoke a persistent approval by id
ŌĆó /yolo: Toggle session YOLO/open mode; hard safety blocks still apply
ŌĆó /cron: Manage scheduled tasks
ŌĆó /trust: Trust this workspace for proactive local work
ŌĆó /untrust: Revoke workspace trust
ŌĆó /workspace.trust.status: Show whether the current workspace is trusted
ŌĆó /doctor: Run a quick in-session health check
ŌĆó /flow: TaskFlow operator commands (status, pause, resume, steer, trace, etc.)
ŌĆó /handoff: Generate a handoff code to share this session with Telegram
ŌĆó /clear: Clear the terminal
ŌĆó /exit: End the session
ŌĆó /version: Show the installed version"
`;

